l = [self.file1, self.file2, self.file3]
h = ['3de8f8b0dc94b8c2230fab9ec0ba0506', '3de8f8b0dc94b8c2230fab9ec0ba0503',
    'aa019ff43c6fdfa1ceeebca9e4a19dfe']
result = verify(l, h)
self.assertTrue(result[self.file1])
self.assertFalse(result[self.file2])
self.assertTrue(result[self.file3])
with self.assertRaises(ValueError):
    verify([self.file1],
        'i am a fake checksum having length not matching any of the known checksums.'
        )
